client_candidates.comment:
Клиент начал работу с Владом Бранишем 01/03/23 и продлевал его работу несколько раз. 13/06 ответил на письмо о том, что недоволен его работой в плане дедлайнов и коммуникации: Hey Svetlana,

Sorry for the late reply, I wanted to see if he was more focused, but unfortunately he still misses almost every deadline and I have had to do some of the work myself to not be in bad focus with our customers. By the way, it is not his skills, those are decent! 
I'll finish the month with him, but I would like to ask you if you have another PPC specialist who can start at the beginning of next month? I'm looking for someone who I can trust working autonomously, as this is one of the core principles we look for.
Coming back to Vladislav, I haven't received the invoice for June jet could you have a look at that as well?

Just got off the phone with two of my clients. They will pause their contract with us in August and probably only will start half of September again. This means I have no work for Tania until then unfortunately :(.

Therefore I unfortunately have to pause our partnership as well. However, I am very happy with the work Tania does and they way she approaches it. So I hope my clients keep to there word and will start again soon so I can hopefully hire Tania again!

Natalia will be responsible for designing approximately 10 pages for a client's website. Many blocks can be reused, and the design work will be conducted using Figma.

The design should follow the new art style provided by the client, which includes new colors, fonts, and logos. The design must be modern and in line with 2024 web design standards.


1) Content Management:

Natalia will manage the layout and design of content, ensuring the blocks align with the client's branding and identity.


2) Collaboration:

She will collaborate closely with Mathieu, who will provide feedback, ideas, and specific examples for the design process.
